19static inline isc_result_t
20fromtext_soa(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
21 isc_token_t token;
22 dns_name_t name;
23 isc_buffer_t buffer;
24 int i;
25 uint32_t n;
26 bool ok;
27
28 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_soa);
29
30 UNUSED(type);
31 UNUSED(rdclass);
32 UNUSED(callbacks);
33
34 if (origin == NULL)
35 origin = dns_rootname;
36
37 for (i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
38 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token,
39 isc_tokentype_string,
40 false));
41
42 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
43 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
44 RETTOK(dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin,
45 options, target));
46 ok = true;
47 if ((options & DNS_RDATA_CHECKNAMES) != 0)
48 switch (i) {
49 case 0:
50 ok = dns_name_ishostname(&name, false);
51 break;
52 case 1:
53 ok = dns_name_ismailbox(&name);
54 break;
55
56 }
57 if (!ok && (options & DNS_RDATA_CHECKNAMESFAIL) != 0)
58 RETTOK(DNS_R_BADNAME);
59 if (!ok && callbacks != NULL)
60 warn_badname(&name, lexer, callbacks);
61 }
62
63 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
64 false));
65 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
66
67 for (i = 0; i < 4; i++) {
68 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token,
69 isc_tokentype_string,
70 false));
71 RETTOK(dns_counter_fromtext(&token.value.as_textregion, &n));
72 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(n, target));
73 }
74
75 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
76}
77
78static const char *soa_fieldnames[5] = {
79 "serial", "refresh", "retry", "expire", "minimum"
80};
81
82static inline isc_result_t
83totext_soa(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
84 isc_region_t dregion;
85 dns_name_t mname;
86 dns_name_t rname;
87 dns_name_t prefix;
88 bool sub;
89 int i;
90 bool multiline;
91 bool comm;
92
93 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_soa);
94 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
95
96 multiline = ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0);
97 if (multiline) {
98 comm = ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_RRCOMMENT) != 0);
99 } else {
100 comm = false;
101 }
102
103
104 dns_name_init(&mname, NULL);
105 dns_name_init(&rname, NULL);
106 dns_name_init(&prefix, NULL);
107
108 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &dregion);
109
110 dns_name_fromregion(&mname, &dregion);
111 isc_region_consume(&dregion, name_length(&mname));
112
113 dns_name_fromregion(&rname, &dregion);
114 isc_region_consume(&dregion, name_length(&rname));
115
116 sub = name_prefix(&mname, tctx->origin, &prefix);
117 RETERR(dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
118
119 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
120
121 sub = name_prefix(&rname, tctx->origin, &prefix);
122 RETERR(dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
123
124 if (multiline)
125 RETERR(str_totext(" (" , target));
126 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
127
128 for (i = 0; i < 5; i++) {
129 char buf[sizeof("0123456789 ; ")];
130 unsigned long num;
131 num = uint32_fromregion(&dregion);
132 isc_region_consume(&dregion, 4);
133 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), comm ? "%-10lu ; " : "%lu", num);
134 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
135 if (comm) {
136 RETERR(str_totext(soa_fieldnames[i], target));
137 /* Print times in week/day/hour/minute/second form */
138 if (i >= 1) {
139 RETERR(str_totext(" (", target));
140 RETERR(dns_ttl_totext(num, true,
141 true, target));
142 RETERR(str_totext(")", target));
143 }
144 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
145 } else if (i < 4) {
146 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
147 }
148 }
149
150 if (multiline)
151 RETERR(str_totext(")", target));
152
153 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
154}

156static inline isc_result_t
157fromwire_soa(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
158 dns_name_t mname;
159 dns_name_t rname;
160 isc_region_t sregion;
161 isc_region_t tregion;
162
163 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_soa);
164
165 UNUSED(type);
166 UNUSED(rdclass);
167
168 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_GLOBAL14);
169
170 dns_name_init(&mname, NULL);
171 dns_name_init(&rname, NULL);
172
173 RETERR(dns_name_fromwire(&mname, source, dctx, options, target));
174 RETERR(dns_name_fromwire(&rname, source, dctx, options, target));
175
176 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sregion);
177 isc_buffer_availableregion(target, &tregion);
178
179 if (sregion.length < 20)
180 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
181 if (tregion.length < 20)
182 return (ISC_R_NOSPACE);
183
184 memmove(tregion.base, sregion.base, 20);
185 isc_buffer_forward(source, 20);
186 isc_buffer_add(target, 20);
187
188 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
189}
190
191static inline isc_result_t
192towire_soa(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
193 isc_region_t sregion;
194 isc_region_t tregion;
195 dns_name_t mname;
196 dns_name_t rname;
197 dns_offsets_t moffsets;
198 dns_offsets_t roffsets;
199
200 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_soa);
201 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
202
203 dns_compress_setmethods(cctx, DNS_COMPRESS_GLOBAL14);
204
205 dns_name_init(&mname, moffsets);
206 dns_name_init(&rname, roffsets);
207
208 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sregion);
209
210 dns_name_fromregion(&mname, &sregion);
211 isc_region_consume(&sregion, name_length(&mname));
212 RETERR(dns_name_towire(&mname, cctx, target));
213
214 dns_name_fromregion(&rname, &sregion);
215 isc_region_consume(&sregion, name_length(&rname));
216 RETERR(dns_name_towire(&rname, cctx, target));
217
218 isc_buffer_availableregion(target, &tregion);
219 if (tregion.length < 20)
220 return (ISC_R_NOSPACE);
221
222 memmove(tregion.base, sregion.base, 20);
223 isc_buffer_add(target, 20);
224 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
225}

227static inline int
228compare_soa(ARGS_COMPARE) {
229 isc_region_t region1;
230 isc_region_t region2;
231 dns_name_t name1;
232 dns_name_t name2;
233 int order;
234
235 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
236 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
237 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_soa);
238 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
239 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
240
241 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
242 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
243
244 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
245 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
246
247 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &region1);
248 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &region2);
249
250 order = dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2);
251 if (order != 0)
252 return (order);
253
254 isc_region_consume(&region1, name_length(&name1));
255 isc_region_consume(&region2, name_length(&name2));
256
257 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
258 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
259
260 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &region1);
261 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &region2);
262
263 order = dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2);
264 if (order != 0)
265 return (order);
266
267 isc_region_consume(&region1, name_length(&name1));
268 isc_region_consume(&region2, name_length(&name2));
269
270 return (isc_region_compare(&region1, &region2));
271}

273static inline isc_result_t
274fromstruct_soa(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
275 dns_rdata_soa_t *soa = source;
276 isc_region_t region;
277
278 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_soa);
279 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
280 REQUIRE(soa->common.rdtype == type);
281 REQUIRE(soa->common.rdclass == rdclass);
282
283 UNUSED(type);
284 UNUSED(rdclass);
285
286 dns_name_toregion(&soa->origin, &region);
287 RETERR(isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
288 dns_name_toregion(&soa->contact, &region);
289 RETERR(isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
290 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(soa->serial, target));
291 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(soa->refresh, target));
292 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(soa->retry, target));
293 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(soa->expire, target));
294 return (uint32_tobuffer(soa->minimum, target));
295}
296
297static inline isc_result_t
298tostruct_soa(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
299 isc_region_t region;
300 dns_rdata_soa_t *soa = target;
301 dns_name_t name;
302 isc_result_t result;
303
304 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_soa);
305 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
306 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
307
308 soa->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
309 soa->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
310 ISC_LINK_INIT(&soa->common, link);
311
312
313 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
314
315 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
316 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
317 isc_region_consume(&region, name_length(&name));
318 dns_name_init(&soa->origin, NULL);
319 RETERR(name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &soa->origin));
320
321 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
322 isc_region_consume(&region, name_length(&name));
323 dns_name_init(&soa->contact, NULL);
324 result = name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &soa->contact);
325 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
326 goto cleanup;
327
328 soa->serial = uint32_fromregion(&region);
329 isc_region_consume(&region, 4);
330
331 soa->refresh = uint32_fromregion(&region);
332 isc_region_consume(&region, 4);
333
334 soa->retry = uint32_fromregion(&region);
335 isc_region_consume(&region, 4);
336
337 soa->expire = uint32_fromregion(&region);
338 isc_region_consume(&region, 4);
339
340 soa->minimum = uint32_fromregion(&region);
341
342 soa->mctx = mctx;
343 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
344
345 cleanup:
346 if (mctx != NULL)
347 dns_name_free(&soa->origin, mctx);
348 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
349}
350
351static inline void
352freestruct_soa(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
353 dns_rdata_soa_t *soa = source;
354
355 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
356 REQUIRE(soa->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_soa);
357
358 if (soa->mctx == NULL)
359 return;
360
361 dns_name_free(&soa->origin, soa->mctx);
362 dns_name_free(&soa->contact, soa->mctx);
363 soa->mctx = NULL;
364}

366static inline isc_result_t
367additionaldata_soa(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
368 UNUSED(rdata);
369 UNUSED(add);
370 UNUSED(arg);
371
372 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_soa);
373
374 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
375}

377static inline isc_result_t
378digest_soa(ARGS_DIGEST) {
379 isc_region_t r;
380 dns_name_t name;
381
382 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_soa);
383
384 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
385
386 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
387 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &r);
388 RETERR(dns_name_digest(&name, digest, arg));
389 isc_region_consume(&r, name_length(&name));
390
391 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
392 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &r);
393 RETERR(dns_name_digest(&name, digest, arg));
394 isc_region_consume(&r, name_length(&name));
395
396 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
397}

399static inline bool
400checkowner_soa(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
401
402 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_soa);
403
404 UNUSED(name);
405 UNUSED(type);
406 UNUSED(rdclass);
407 UNUSED(wildcard);
408
409 return (true);
410}
411
412static inline bool
413checknames_soa(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
414 isc_region_t region;
415 dns_name_t name;
416
417 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_soa);
418
419 UNUSED(owner);
420
421 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
422 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
423 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
424 if (!dns_name_ishostname(&name, false)) {
425 if (bad != NULL)
426 dns_name_clone(&name, bad);
427 return (false);
428 }
429 isc_region_consume(&region, name_length(&name));
430 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
431 if (!dns_name_ismailbox(&name)) {
432 if (bad != NULL)
433 dns_name_clone(&name, bad);
434 return (false);
435 }
436 return (true);
437}

439static inline int
440casecompare_soa(ARGS_COMPARE) {
441 return (compare_soa(rdata1, rdata2));
442}
